To run the mov -> mp4 converter, run

	./convert_mp4.rb BASE_DIR INPUT_DIR

and it will convert all files in INPUT_DIR, placing them in a mp4 folder relative to BASE_DIR

e.g.

	./convert_mp4.rb /Volumes/Data/Library/ /Volumes/Data/Library/TV\ Shows

or
	./convert_mp4.rb /Volumes/Data/Library/ /Volumes/Data/Library/TV\ Shows/The\ Wire/Season\ Two
